          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "From reaction kinetics and Q-values it is seen that",
                "alpha-particles from Ni-58(n,an')and Ni-58(n,n'a) can",
                "have energies only below 8 MeV. From the experimental",
                "alpha spectrum it is apparent that about 50% of",
                "the total alpha-particles.",
                "The evaporation spectrum from the statistical plot for",
                "the reactions Ni-58(n,a) and Ni-58(n,an') shows that",
                "only about 30% of the alpha-particles falls",
                "below 8MeV.",
                "From these considerations it is estimated that the",
                "cross-section for the reaction Ni-58(n,n'a) is about",
                "20% of the total cross-section for all the",
                "three reactions,i.e.about 36 mb."
              ]
            }
          ],
